        "Journal of Statistical Software, 36(13), 1-17.",
        "URL http://www.jstatsoft.org/v36/i13/."),
	
  header       = "To cite rpanel's spatial teaching tools (rp.geosim, rp.mururoa, rp.firth) use:"
